This model uses 20% of the 🎹 Spotify Tracks Dataset found at this link: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/maharshipandya/-spotify-tracks-dataset

The deployed app runs UIsmall.py and runs at this link below:
https://spotify-bridge-small.streamlit.app/

General Info (folders):
- data/ → raw and processed datasets
- models/ → saved models
- notebook/ → exploration and testing (dummy)
- src/ → source code (python files)
